        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix: chat/message bug sweep — history, Discord reply, build, session resolve",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nFour independent bug classes affecting chat and message delivery, identified and fixed by OpenClaw self-check sweep:\n\n- **History resolution**: `sessions_history(current)` returned empty when active transcripts lived in `*.jsonl.reset.*` siblings. Added fallback and `usageFamilySessionIds` backfill.\n- **Discord visible reply**: `messageProvider`/`channel` misalignment caused `message` tool to drop from sandbox allowlist. Strengthened `shouldForceMessageTool()` and prioritized delivery channel over `webchat`/`internal` provider label.\n- **Build/dist integrity**: Pre-build cleanup deleted hashed chunks that stable aliases still referenced, causing `ERR_MODULE_NOT_FOUND` at runtime. Stopped aggressive root chunk pruning.\n- **Current session resolve**: `sessions.resolve(\"current\")` failed when gateway had no connection-to-session reverse lookup. Added subscription registry.\n\n## Verification\n\n- Implementation by OpenClaw self-check sweep on local source tree\n- Unit tests added/updated for each fix area\n- Build verified locally\n- Live gateway E2E confirmation pending (gateway restart blocked in sandbox at time of fix; now unblocked)\n\n## Files changed (28)\n\nGrouped by fix area:\n\n**A. History resolution**: `session-utils.fs.ts`, `server-methods/chat.ts` + tests\n**B. Discord reply**: `run-attempt.ts`, `attempt-execution.ts`, `pi-embedded-runner/attempt.ts`, `tools-effective-inventory.ts` + tests\n**C. Build integrity**: `scripts/tsdown-build.mjs` + test\n**D. Session resolve**: `server-chat-state.ts`, `server.impl.ts`, `sessions-resolve.ts`, `server-request-context.ts`, `server-methods/sessions.ts`, `shared-types.ts` + tests\n**Other**: `pi-tools.ts`, `task-registry.store.sqlite.ts`, `ui/controllers/chat.ts` + tests\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [ ] Verify build passes on CI\n- [ ] Verify existing test suite passes\n- [ ] Live gateway restart + Discord channel visible reply E2E\n- [ ] Session history after `/new` rotation",
